EVENT HALL
DUPLEX
WATER FACTORY
This is an event hall designed and constructed for Engr. Fabiyi,
who is a real estate mogul, resident in Abuja, Nigeria.
The project is Located beside Landmark University in Omu-
Aran, Kwara State.
During my tenure as the Head of the Design Office within the
Directorate of Physical Planning and Development at Landmark
University.
I played a key role in both the original design and construction
supervision of the water factory project.
Situated on the university campus in Omu-Aran, Kwara State,
this project was of paramount importance in enhancing the
institution's infrastructure.
LMU DUPLEX
The 4-bedroom duplex, strategically located on the university

in Omu-Aran, Kwara State, was a pivotal addition to the institution's

Within this context, I, as the Head of the Design Office within the
